Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临\N我是今天负责的吉川莲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力在这个完美的空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为客人去除疲劳请慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（超高级治愈按摩）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面我叫吉川莲 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个给你放松吧 可能有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该就可以放松了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要用按摩油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么是热的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太热的话要告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热吗 没事吧 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痒吗 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常来这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里很敏感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头真的硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 轮到另一边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多用一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手真大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我的大好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么下半身也要开始按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在乱动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要伸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你放松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人这里需要排毒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就会引起很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点按摩这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要脱掉了 害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把手拿开吧 用一点按摩油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么夸张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我要准备下一个 按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用这个特别的按摩油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为男性性器是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有能量的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以把手拿开吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续浇上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 感受到能量了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要进行下一个步骤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得好热了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要激烈一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会温柔点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那应要继续下一个步骤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把腿给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始释放能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越热了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.31,0:24:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.58,0:25:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要开始下一个步骤了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.74,0:26:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.88,0:26:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.30,0:26:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.32,0:26:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时按摩上半身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.45,0:28:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.40,0:28:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.41,0:28:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人也可以动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.56,0:29:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.13,0:30:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.81,0:30:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换一个姿势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.64,0:31:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人也可以动一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.60,0:31:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.31,0:32:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要从后面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.25,0:32:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽插我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以随便动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.27,0:33:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请继续抽插我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.25,0:34:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.74,0:39:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.01,0:39:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.49,0:39:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的呢 -很久没见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.50,0:40:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-完全都不来呢\N-因为太忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.58,0:40:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要来了吗 -失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.31,0:40:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-冷吗 -刚刚好啊 多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-多一点吗 -没错多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.99,0:40:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-舒服吗 -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.07,0:40:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多用一点泡沬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真骨啊 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.87,0:40:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手也抹上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.01,0:40:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好棒 -开始摸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这么漂亮的胸部当然要摸啊\N-别这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.89,0:40:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这样舒服吗 -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.17,0:41:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.11,0:41:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-乳头很敏感对吗 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.45,0:41:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.59,0:41:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.19,0:41:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.39,0:41:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗 -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.26,0:41:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太好了 太好了 这个\N-怎么了 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.27,0:41:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-用太多了吧 好冷 -当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.61,0:41:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.88,0:41:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.02,0:41:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-等等 不要   -为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.03,0:42:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我给你洗干净哦 -等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.77,0:42:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有感觉了吧\N-才不是 你太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.78,0:42:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.31,0:42:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点坏呢 会做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.25,0:42:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那么 这样呢  -出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.46,0:42:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是想要这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.67,0:42:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.81,0:43:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这样摸不是最好吗\N-虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.02,0:43:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笔等 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.85,0:43:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要继续工作啊\N-那么我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.90,0:43:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.90,0:43:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我都想要动了  -等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.84,0:43:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.39,0:43:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.26,0:43:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-乳头摩擦到了哦 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.40,0:43:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摩擦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.34,0:43:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.61,0:44:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不只是乳头 那里摩擦到了\N-感觉到了吗 都变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.95,0:44:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.10,0:44:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.71,0:44:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-都看光了啊\N-被看光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.78,0:44:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这里什么都没穿吗\N-讨厌 别张开
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.92,0:44:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.59,0:44:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-原来可以吗 -别张太开
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.40,0:44:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.67,0:45:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么一直在摸   -忍耐不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.21,0:45:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不摸的话不好吧 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.02,0:45:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.42,0:45:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行 -不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.70,0:45:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-屁股好滑 -才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.79,0:45:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.11,0:45:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.58,0:45:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.26,0:46:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-变大了呢 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.40,0:46:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全还不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.94,0:46:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒硬得不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.59,0:46:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不会摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.29,0:46:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-以为你要摸了 -还不摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.78,0:46:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.51,0:46:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好舒服 -继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.87,0:47:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你会想摸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.80,0:47:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才 没有想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.41,0:47:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.81,0:47:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.88,0:47:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.29,0:47:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.15,0:47:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.70,0:47:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有点冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.23,0:47:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.58,0:47:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.51,0:47:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-肉棒肯定是这样啊\N-好温暖 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.39,0:48:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.86,0:48:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗 -太想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.47,0:48:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.08,0:48:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.84,0:48:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.45,0:49:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太快了吧 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.86,0:49:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.95,0:49:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好厉害 -怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.81,0:49:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-舒服吗？  -但是可以继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.49,0:49:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.47,0:50:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-站起来吧 -差点就射了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.24,0:50:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行了 -小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.92,0:50:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-肉棒还是很硬哦 -的确
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.54,0:50:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-已经好了吧 -的确
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.01,0:50:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒洗干净就差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.82,0:50:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好厉害 -为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.69,0:50:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还有这边 这边\N-好的 屁股对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.70,0:51:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好像已经好了\N-对了 你也要洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.98,0:51:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -这边洗干净了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.98,0:51:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.52,0:51:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不洗干净不行呢\N-的确 都是泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.66,0:51:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对了 还有这边 -这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.74,0:51:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.41,0:51:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好像可以了吧 -差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.83,0:51:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.56,0:52:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-舔肉棒 -在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.83,0:52:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要在这里做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.90,0:52:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么稍微舔一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.29,0:52:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.20,0:52:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.34,0:52:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢硬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.05,0:53:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那么 回去吧 -要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.19,0:53:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.06,0:53:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-需要脱掉吗 -果然很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.76,0:54:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那么要舔了 -请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.84,0:54:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那边开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.79,0:54:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.67,0:55:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.08,0:55:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-和你的话可能忍耐不了多久\N-才没有这种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.36,0:55:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.83,0:55:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-想舔很久了啊 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.41,0:55:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-因为忍耐很久了\N-的确 流淫水了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.83,0:55:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.85,0:55:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.46,0:55:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.66,0:55:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这里也有 太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.13,0:56:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.40,0:56:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.14,0:56:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都舔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.08,0:56:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.15,0:56:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.42,0:56:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.16,0:56:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那么继续舔吧 -什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.73,0:57:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这个 真的不行 -舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.55,0:57:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想舔那里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.17,0:57:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.37,0:57:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我想舔啊 过来这边   -要舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.39,0:58:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太粗暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.06,0:58:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-闻一下好了 -别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.47,0:58:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.61,0:58:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要舔 肯定会摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.41,0:59:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.45,1:00:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都湿透了 我想插进去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.53,1:00:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.86,1:00:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进去吧 那么
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.00,1:00:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-躺下来吧 -好的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.61,1:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太期持了 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.95,1:00:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这样挑逗你好吗 -报复我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.29,1:00:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行吗 -不行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.09,1:00:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.50,1:01:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.20,1:01:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好厉害 肉棒好舒服\N-讨厌 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.36,1:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.03,1:02:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.91,1:02:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.92,1:02:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-乳头都硬了   -一直在摸呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.22,1:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.37,1:03:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.39,1:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续让你高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.93,1:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这个角度不一样吧\N-那里不行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.50,1:04:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.04,1:04:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.71,1:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以激烈一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.79,1:04:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.99,1:04:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.40,1:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.66,1:05:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.82,1:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.29,1:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就喜欢这种吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.56,1:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.51,1:06:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报复
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.30,1:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你做得到吗 -当然了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.66,1:07:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.19,1:07:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.60,1:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.49,1:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是要报复我吗\N-你怎么在动
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.31,1:07:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我快忍耐不住了 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.93,1:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.26,1:08:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的啊 -继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.40,1:08:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要吗 还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.94,1:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我快忍耐不住了 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.08,1:08:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么啊 -等等
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.82,1:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.97,1:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.78,1:09:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很开心吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.41,1:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样舔乳头真的受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.41,1:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头很敏感吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.28,1:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太棒了 -我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.90,1:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-变硬了 -我忍耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.45,1:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-等等 不行了 不行了\N-不行吗 投降了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.94,1:10:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.90,1:11:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
