Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.36,1:36:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不痒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.23,1:36:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.70,1:36:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.53,1:37:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.24,1:37:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.99,1:38:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.13,1:38:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.40,1:38:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了促进血流畅通
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.10,1:38:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始摸龟头了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.61,1:40:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从下往上
