Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.16,1:46:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.03,1:46:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以插进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.90,1:46:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.98,1:46:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗 -要试一试吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.84,1:49:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.97,1:54:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.17,1:54:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.83,1:55:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.23,1:55:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.22,1:56:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.66,1:58:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.53,1:59:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好厉害 好舒服 -好热
